Quentin Dolmaire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quentin_Dolmaire 0 Quentin Dolmaire (born 18 February 1994) is a French actor. He was nominated for the César Award for Most Promising Actor in 2016 for his role in My Golden Days. Quentin_Dolmaire ( born 18_February_1994 ) is a_French_actor .
